document_data.Notable Speakers:
* [[Arkaneus Silvermane]], the [[Archdruid]] of [[Mosstone]].
* [[Brandywine Furfoot]], a [[halfling]] [[cleric]] who worked at the [[As The Vine Twines]] vineyard in [[Ravens Bluff]] in the late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].<ref>{{Cite polyhedron/62/The Living City: As The Vine Twines|17}}
* [[Martha Tanner]], a [[gnome]] [[illusionist]] that worked at the [[Jack Mooney & Sons Circus]].<ref>
* Captain [[Silas Windspray]] and his first mate [[Judy Longbow]] both spoke Lizardman, allowing them to communicate with their lizardman navigator [[Ssissilif]].<ref>{{Cite organized play/LC/Waterfalls|12}}<ref>{{Cite organized play/LC/A Spell of Bad Weather|6}}
* [[Thanthal]], a [[human]] [[mage]] and former [[adventurer]] who at the Jack Mooney & Sons Circus.<ref>
* [[Vernon Condor]], the city of Ravens Bluff's [[Regent of the Exchequer]] in the late 14{{th}} century DR.<ref>
